# Frontend Monorepo (Turborepo)

Turborepo with `apps/*` workspaces (powered by `__PM__`).

```
frontend/
├── turbo.json
├── package.json
└── apps/
    └── <name>/
```

## Scripts (run from `frontend/`)

```bash
__PM__ install
__PM__ run dev      # turbo run dev  (all apps in parallel)
__PM__ run build    # turbo run build
__PM__ run lint
__PM__ run start
```

Or use the root CLI:

```bash
mx add:fe <name>
mx run fe <name> dev
mx run all dev   # backend + frontend together
```
